data.description: Welcome to Marco Polo Village, a 55+ adult community.  Well maintained, newly painted 1-story traditional home offers 530sf screened Florida Room with lots of distinctive architectural lines all on nearly 3/4 of an acre!  The extra large concrete driveway leads to your 3-car screened garage with over 800SF!  Foyer is open to the dining room and living room with arched windows and lots of light.  Equipped stainless steel kitchen with granite countertops and kitchen island for extra storage & functionality.  French door leads to expansive patio area with stone-like tile & screened enclosure.  Master bedroom with tray ceiling offers an inviting en suite with whirlpool tub, separate toilet, shower, double sinks and sky blue porcelain floor.  Hardwood & tile floors throughout.  Move-in ready!
